    h1 Drm Dropdown Buttons

    p Show or hide a menu when a button is clicked. Available in solid or split buttons.

    h2 Live Demo 

    .example-holder
        .drm-dropdown-solid-btn-holder
            button Info
            ul
                li: a(href="#") Info 1
                li: a(href="#") Info 2
                li: a(href="#") Info 3
                li.divider
                li: a(href="#") Info 4
                
        .drm-dropdown-solid-btn-holder
            button More Info
            ul
                li: a.text-disabled(href="#") Info 1
                li: a(href="#") Info 2
                li: a(href="#") Info 3
                li: a(href="#") Info 4

        .drm-dropdown-solid-btn-holder
            button Click Me!
            ul
                li: a(href="#") Info 1
                li: a(href="#") Info 2
                li: a(href="#") Info 3
                li: a(href="#") Info 4 

    .example-holder
        .drm-dropdown-split-btn-holder
            .drm-dropdown-button-group
                button Alert
                button &#9662;
                ul
                    li: a(href="#") Info 1
                    li: a(href="#") Info 2
                    li: a(href="#") Info 3
                    li: a(href="#") Info 4
                
        .drm-dropdown-split-btn-holder
            .drm-dropdown-button-group
                button This Is Another Alert
                button &#9662;
                ul
                    li: a(href="#") Info 1
                    li: a(href="#") Info 2
